620"><span class="csE736517A">(6) Board of Banking and Financial Institutions provided in &sect;31A-3-1 </span><span class="cs50A3B802">et seq</span><span class="csE736517A">. of this code;</span></p><p class="cs45E53620"><span class="csE736517A">(7) Lending and Credit Rate Board provided in &sect;47A-1-1 </span><span class="cs50A3B802">et seq</span><span class="csE736517A">. of this code;</span></p><p class="cs45E53620"><span class="csE736517A">(8) Division of Financial Institutions provided in &sect;31A-2-1 </span><span class="cs50A3B802">et seq</span><span class="csE736517A">. of this code;</span></p><p class="cs45E53620"><span class="csE736517A">(9) The State Budget Office provided in &sect;11B-2-1 </span><span class="cs50A3B802">et seq</span><span class="csE736517A">. of this code;</span></p><p class="cs45E53620"><span class="csE736517A">(10) The Municipal Bond Commission provided in &sect;13-3-1 </span><span class="cs50A3B802">et seq</span><span class="csE736517A">. of this code;</span></p><p class="cs45E53620"><span class="csE736517A">(11) The Office of Tax Appeals provided in &sect;11-10A-1 </span><span class="cs50A3B802">et seq</span><span class="csE736517A">. of this code; and</span></p><p class="cs45E53620"><span class="csE736517A">(12) The State Athletic Commission provided in &sect;29-5A-1 </span><span class="cs50A3B802">et seq</span><span class="csE736517A">. of this code. </span></p><p class="cs45E53620"><span class="csB2FCAD92">&nbsp;(l) </span><span class="csF2E808A1">(k)</span><span class="csE736517A"> The following agencies and boards, including all of the allied, advisory, affiliated, or related entities and funds associated with any agency or board, are incorporated in and administered as a part of the Department of Transportation:</span></p><p class="cs45E53620"><span class="csE736517A">(1) Division of Highways provided in &sect;17-2A-1 </span><span class="cs50A3B802">et seq</span><span class="csE736517A">. of this code;</span></p><p class="cs4